- Both are same but the syntax of Arrow Function is different.
the syntax is 

            let Arfunc = () => {
                console.log("hello Arrow Function")
            }
            Arfunc()
 
   - The difference main of function fom the Arrow function is:

            Function func (){
                console.log("hello Function")
            }
            func()

